title: PES2014 ME Pal Xbox360 - Biryani
description:
Pro Evolution Soccer 2014 with arabic commentary!

same goes for this one, run first in abgx360 before burning on dvd or ectracting to RGH/JTAG. 


Pro Evolution's next installment comes with more realism and thrilling gameplay than ever before. PES 2014 promises better ball control, new tactics and character animations that will make you feel as if you are in fact in the field!

Pro Evolution is one of the most anticipated soccer games yet, featuring enhanced graphics, improved ball physics and much more. The game's new Motion Animation Stability System makes characters collide with each other more realistically and alter their balance. Fans of PES' multiplayer feature would be pleased to know that they can customize their player tactics in key positions on the field with the help of 3 players or more. The AI is now much smarter and more predictive, so don't be afraid to pass the ball to them. Enjoy intense Arabic commentary featuring voices of famous Arab sports commentators!

Enjoy another Football game with arabic commentary!

- Biryani
